column5: Great video Steve. Thanks for sharing!  Jealous that I'm not out there pounding the big ones like you
Nice Job, Thats some productive fishing!!! Looks like your having lots of fun!!
Great vid Steve. Are finding more naturals then stockers this season? Definitly can see the difference it the body colors in the fish.

Great job and nice vid coverage Steve!.  Fishing has been nothing short of awesome so far this season... if you see me and the Argo out on the main lake come over and say hi... I live out there Fri, Sat and Sun. Looks like a softwater date to share a boat together. Continued success on 'spank'n dem fish!

The past few years I've noticed an even mix of naturals and stockers, which is awesome to see.  One thing that has been far more prevalent this season, is the lakers regurgitating herring.  Big 9-13 inchers.  They're chewing out there and staying healthy!And Greg, lets do it buddy!
Awesome video, felt like we were right there  fishing with you .
